		<title>Kling AI Raises $2.8 Billion in $18 Billion Valuation Backed By Alibaba &#038; Tencent</title>
		<link>https://ventureburn.com/kling-ai-raises-2-8-billion-with-alibaba-backing/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Ekemini]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 17:44:02 +0000</pubDate>
