										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The competitive arena is officially open as Binance unrolls its latest high-stakes token event on the early-stage listing platform, Binance Alpha. The </span><b>Binance Traders League Season 3 – Sentient (SENT) Trading Challenge</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> has arrived, giving verified users and VIP tiers a premier opportunity to test their market tactics on the SENT token and secure exclusive rewards.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The trading league spans a tight window, running for exactly one week:</span></p>
<ul>
