</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This comprehensive guide details the structure, entry milestones, and rewards hierarchy needed to successfully lock in your portion of the massive </span><b>20,000,000 SENT token voucher prize pool</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">. If you are new to the platform, use our exclusive Binance Referral Code to unlock trading fee rebates and prepare your Web3 account for upcoming distribution events!</span></p>
