</a></p>
<h2><b>Tournament Eligibility &amp; Trading Parameters</b></h2>
<div id="attachment_77227" style="width: 1210px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-77227" class="size-full wp-image-77227" src="https://chainplay.gg/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/f991fa543cbac525d765f3908e14acb8.jpeg" alt="Binance Sent Trading Challenge" width="1200" height="628" /><p id="caption-attachment-77227" class="wp-caption-text">Binance Sent Trading Challenge</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Understanding who can participate and which asset pathways qualify is vital to optimizing your daily turnover metrics. Below are the official tournament parameters:</span></p>
<h3><b>Participant Eligibility:</b></h3>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Qualified Traders:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> All verified new users, regular users, and all Binance VIP accounts are fully eligible to compete.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Exclusion Restrictions:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Market makers enrolled in the Binance Spot Liquidity Provider Program and all Binance Brokers are strictly barred from participating.</span></li>
</ul>
<h3><b>Eligible Altcoin Trading Pairs:</b></h3>
<ul>
